attributes.title: OBA Uganda
attributes.description:
Created on April 19, 2010 by bbellows on Sourcemap.org:

Vouchers are distributed in villages across 22 districts of western Uganda to low income women who can then use the voucher for maternal healthcare in contracted facilities.
